abstract: Florida State football running back Dalvin Cook is found not guilty of misdemeanor battery charge stemming from accusations he hit woman outside Tallahassee, Fla, bar in June 2015.
lead_paragraph: Dalvin Cook was found not guilty of punching a woman outside a Tallahassee, Fla., bar in June.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | College Football; Florida State Player Cleared
